vaddu bava thappu ( english : no brother-in-law it 's wrong ) is a 1994 telugu , comedy film produced by p.purshothama rao , c.kalyan on sri ammulya art productions banner and directed by k.ajay kumar . starring rajendra prasad , ravali , indraja in the lead roles and music composed by vidyasagar . the film is the remake of the marathi film kiss bai kiss ( 1988 ) which was first remade in hindi as honeymoon ( 1992 ) . the film recorded as flop at box office .